      "question": "When calcium carbonate is heated, it decomposes into:",
      "options": [
        "CaO + O2",
        "CaO + CO2",
        "Ca + CO2",
        "Ca + O2"
      ],
      "explanation": "CaCO3 (on heating) -> CaO + CO2. This is a thermal decomposition reaction. Quicklime (CaO) is produced."
    },
